<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="315" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,151,1509]" pageId="12" pageNumber="315">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,314,1196,1221]" pageId="12" pageNumber="315">Diagnosis</emphasis>
. New species is similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="Zheng, 2003" authorityName="Zheng &amp; Ou" authorityYear="2003" box="[636,1084,1196,1221]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Bolivaritettix" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="315" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hutiaoxiana">
<emphasis box="[636,929,1196,1220]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="315">Bolivaritettix hutiaoxiana</emphasis>
Zheng, 2003
</taxonomicName>
from which it differs in body small-sized, length of pronotum 
<specimenCount box="[516,536,1232,1256]" pageId="12" pageNumber="315" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
10.0 mm– 
<quantity box="[653,752,1231,1256]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.05" pageId="12" pageNumber="315" unit="mm" value="10.5">10.5 mm</quantity>
, 
<specimenCount box="[764,785,1233,1256]" pageId="12" pageNumber="315" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
<quantity box="[792,892,1231,1256]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.15" pageId="12" pageNumber="315" unit="mm" value="11.5">11.5 mm</quantity>
–12.0 mm (body large-sized, length of pronotum 
<specimenCount box="[151,171,1268,1293]" pageId="12" pageNumber="315" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
16.0 mm, 
<specimenCount box="[285,300,1268,1292]" pageId="12" pageNumber="315" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
17.0 mm in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Ou" authorityYear="2003" box="[439,604,1268,1292]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Bolivaritettix" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="315" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hutiaoxiana">
<emphasis box="[439,604,1268,1292]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="315">B. hutiaoxiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); antenna inserted below lower margins of eyes (antenna inserted between lower margins of eyes in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Ou" authorityYear="2003" box="[431,595,1304,1328]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Bolivaritettix" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="315" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hutiaoxiana">
<emphasis box="[431,595,1304,1328]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="315">B. hutiaoxiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); upper margin of pronotum slightly undulate before shoulders and straight behind shoulders in profile (upper margin of pronotum straight in profile in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Ou" authorityYear="2003" box="[1072,1243,1340,1364]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Bolivaritettix" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="315" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hutiaoxiana">
<emphasis box="[1072,1243,1340,1364]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="315">B. hutiaoxiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); caudal end of pronotum reaching apex of hind tibia (caudal end of pronotum reaching two-thirds of hind tibia in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Ou" authorityYear="2003" box="[1254,1419,1376,1400]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Bolivaritettix" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="315" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hutiaoxiana">
<emphasis box="[1254,1419,1376,1400]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="315">B. hutiaoxiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); hind tibia dark brown, with light brown at base and middle (hind tibia dark brown in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Ou" authorityYear="2003" box="[1103,1268,1412,1436]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Bolivaritettix" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="315" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hutiaoxiana">
<emphasis box="[1103,1268,1412,1436]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="315">B. hutiaoxiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
